library(readxl)
data_NK <- read_excel(path = "~/Dropbox/Reaserch/Methods_Statistics/2016-12/Results_NKE-4_20161212.xlsx", sheet = "compile")
data_NK$Cluster_4 <- as.character(data_NK$Cluster_4)
data_NK$Cluster_5 <- as.character(data_NK$Cluster_5)

library(ggplot2)
ggplot(data_NK, aes(x = Cu_mean, y = Zn_mean)) +
  geom_point() +
  ggtitle("Cu vs. Zn Concentration (with coh ratio)") +
  xlab("Cu/coh") +
  ylab("Zn/coh") +
  geom_smooth(method = "lm")

theme()scale_color_hue()

ggplot(data_NK, aes(x = Cu_mean, y = Zn_mean, color = Cluster_5)) +
  geom_point() +
  ggtitle("Cu vs. Zn Concentration (with coh ratio)") +
  xlab("Cu/coh") +
  ylab("Zn/coh") +
  scale_color_hue(name ="No. of Clusters") +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(face = "bold", family = "Times", hjust = 0.5), 
        axis.title = element_text(face = "bold", family = "Times"),
        legend.position = "top", legend.title = element_text(face = "italic", family = "Times"), 
        legend.text = element_text(family = "Times"),
        axis.text = element_text(family = "Times"))

scale_shape()

ggplot(data_NK, aes(x = Cu_mean, y = Zn_mean, shape = Cluster_5)) +
  geom_point() +
  ggtitle("Cu vs. Zn Concentration (with coh ratio)") +
  xlab("Cu/coh") +
  ylab("Zn/coh") +
  scale_shape(name ="No. of Clusters") +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(face = "bold", family = "Times", hjust = 0.5), 
        axis.title = element_text(face = "bold", family = "Times"),
        legend.position = "top", legend.title = element_text(face = "italic", family = "Times"), 
        legend.text = element_text(family = "Times"),
        axis.text = element_text(family = "Times"))

ggplot(data_NK, aes(x = `position (mm)`, y = Zn_mean, color = Cluster_5)) +
  #geom_point(size = 1) +
  geom_line() +
  ggtitle("Zn Concentration with Position") +
  xlab("Position (mm)") +
  ylab("Zn/coh") +
  scale_color_hue(name ="No. of Clusters") +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(face = "bold", family = "Times", hjust = 0.5), 
        axis.title = element_text(face = "bold", family = "Times"),
        legend.position = "top", legend.title = element_text(face = "italic", family = "Times"), 
        legend.text = element_text(family = "Times"),
        axis.text = element_text(family = "Times"))

ggplot(data_NK, aes(x = `position (mm)`, y = Zn_mean)) +
  #geom_point(size = 1) +
  geom_line() +
  ggtitle("Zn Concentration with Position") +
  xlab("Position (mm)") +
  ylab("Zn/coh") +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(face = "bold", family = "Times", hjust = 0.5, size = 20, color = "#333333"), 
        axis.title = element_text(face = "bold", family = "Times", size = 14, color = "#333333"),
        axis.text = element_text(family = "Times", size = 12, color = "#333333"))

ggplot(data_NK, aes(x = Zn_mean)) +
  geom_histogram(binwidth = 0.05) +
  ggtitle("Concentration Distribution of Zn") +
  xlab("Zn/coh") +
  ylab("Count") +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(face = "bold", family = "Times", hjust = 0.5, size = 20, color = "#333333"),
        axis.title = element_text(face = "bold", family = "Times", size = 14, color = "#333333"),
        axis.text = element_text(family = "Times", size = 12, color = "#333333"))

guides() facet_wrap()

ggplot(data_NK, aes(x = Zn_mean, color = Cluster_5)) +
  geom_histogram(binwidth = 0.02) +
  ggtitle("Concentration Distribution of Zn in Different Clusters") +
  xlab("Zn/coh") +
  ylab("Count") +
  scale_color_hue(name ="No. of Clusters") +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(face = "bold", family = "Times", hjust = 0.5, size = 20, color = "#333333"),
        axis.title = element_text(face = "bold", family = "Times", size = 14, color = "#333333"),
        axis.text.x = element_text(family= "Times", size = 10, color = "#333333"),
        axis.text.y = element_text(family= "Times", size = 12, color = "#333333"),
        legend.title = element_text(face = "bold.italic", family = "Times", color = "#333333"),
        legend.position = c(0.8, 0.2)) +
  guides(color = guide_legend(nrow = 2, override.aes = list(size = 4))) +
  facet_wrap(~ Cluster_5)

5lab()
